== 製作 ==
2016年1月，據透露，[[亞當·崔佛|亞當·崔佛]]和[[席芬坦·法拉哈尼|席芬坦·法拉哈尼]]將共同於[[吉姆·賈木許|吉姆·賈木許]]執導和編劇的電影中合作。製片商K5 Film的奧利佛·賽門與丹尼爾·鮑爾將作為執行製片人，而Animal Kingdom的喬書亞·阿斯特拉罕和卡特·羅根則會擔任監製一職<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/01/adam-driver-to-star-in-jim-jarmuschs-paterson-amazon-and-k5-to-co-finance-1201681250/|title=Adam Driver To Star In Jim Jarmusch’s ‘Paterson’, Amazon And K5 To Co-Finance|first=Ali|last=Jafaar|date=2016-01-13|accessdate=2016-05-05|archive-date=2017-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170429140743/http://deadline.com/2016/01/adam-driver-to-star-in-jim-jarmuschs-paterson-amazon-and-k5-to-co-finance-1201681250/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
[[File:Cannes_2016_25.jpg|thumb]]、[[席芬坦·法拉哈尼|席芬坦·法拉哈尼]]和[[吉姆·賈木許|吉姆·賈木許]]出席於2016年的[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]]]
電影最先於2016年5月16日在[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]上作全球首映<ref name="IW"/><ref name="VarCannes"/>。{{le|亞馬遜影業|Amazon Studios}}獲得了電影的美國發行權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/01/12/casting-net-adam-driver-jim-jarmusch|title=Casting Net: Adam Driver joins Jim Jarmusch comedy Paterson|publisher=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|first=Will|last=Robinson|date=2016-01-12|accessdate=2016-05-05|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211171225/https://ew.com/article/2016/01/12/casting-net-adam-driver-jim-jarmusch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。後來宣布，{{le|Bleecker Street (公司)|Bleecker Street (company)|Bleecker Street}}和亞馬遜影業共同合作負責定於2016年12月28日在美國上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/adam-driver-paterson-release-date-1201822050/|title=Adam Driver’s ‘Paterson’ Gets Awards-Season Release Date (EXCLUSIVE)|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Brent|last=Lang|date=2016-07-25|accessdate=2016-07-25|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108152940/https://variety.com/2016/film/news/adam-driver-paterson-release-date-1201822050/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 評價 ===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度高達97%，基於36條評論，平均分為9.1/10<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/paterson/|title=Paterson (2016)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2016-09-14|archive-date=2021-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210402030056/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/paterson|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到87分，代表「普遍好評」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/paterson|title=Paterson|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2016-09-14|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112011747/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/paterson|dead-url=no}}</ref>，收穫普遍讚譽。

